# webpb conventions

Before editing code or tests, read the matching doc under `ai-kit/`:

- Java production code: `ai-kit/CODE_CONVENTIONS.md`
- Java / Vitest tests: `ai-kit/TEST_CONVENTIONS.md`
- Go plugin golden tests: `ai-kit/GO_TEST_CONVENTIONS.md`

Key rules:

- Java control flow always uses braced blocks on their own line.
- Tests are behavior-first: `should ... when ...`; at most one `@Nested` level.
- Codegen golden tests live in `plugin` (Go) only — do not add duplicate JUnit golden suites.

After Java changes: `./gradlew spotlessApply && ./gradlew build`.
